			    </div>
			    <br>
			    <div class="second-paragraph">
			        Our main objective is to promote a reliable information environment and to combat the spread of false, manipulated or misleading news. We are committed to providing users with tools to identify and report misinformation.
			    </div>
			    <br>
			    <div>
